    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the two sides but that feels like a bit of an answer for both and neither lol. like if you look at the actual data and the way most developed nations handle it, isn't it pretty clear that the \"human right\" argument is the more morally sound and effective approach? why do people still push the government takeover narrative?",
